{"tid":1949230,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"END 終於要完..要幸福","createTime":"2020-03-29T13:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T14:22:06.000Z","uid":8454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9544d65681fa75c9e6417d9d1b0d3945c15dbc4f","tid":1949230,"uid":8454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:26:48.000Z","msg":"係今日 終於叫咗一位共同朋友 睇你既ig<br />\n呢位朋友亦cap咗圖比我 終於見到你搵到屬於你既幸福<br />\n既開心亦心痛 我以為我已經唔會再咁痛<br />\n但原來當睇完知道 自己個心原來仍然係咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦明白 同你再唔會任何契機 唔會有啲咩而搵大家<br />\n不過我都想講 你係應該值得更好 <br />\n你唔要我其實係啱<br />\n記住 要開心幸福落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思咁多位 只係想舒發吓 勿屌 謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6423ef558c7075dd32e5ed23865cfec9b2cf40b3","tid":1949230,"uid":248493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"女死女還在 下個更可愛"},{"pid":"d752b796b953daf8a6ba64b2c152b5f397d7a801","tid":1949230,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🥱</span></div>"},{"pid":"90979c037e1c1ee2e76f70875b9255ddd1d0dc0b","tid":1949230,"uid":8454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6423ef558c7075dd32e5ed23865cfec9b2cf40b3","tid":1949230,"uid":248493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"女死女還在 下個更可愛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"謝謝 我明啊 不過我諗需要比較多時間"},{"pid":"0de0feb9c842ad5029983eb1d77b81817b37c752","tid":1949230,"uid":134095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90979c037e1c1ee2e76f70875b9255ddd1d0dc0b","tid":1949230,"uid":8454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6423ef558c7075dd32e5ed23865cfec9b2cf40b3","tid":1949230,"uid":248493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl